{
  "stem": "15577.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And by this removing of the factory-- textile factory machines, Czech workers who worked in the factory worked with us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Oh, they were demounting the machines, and we were only helping.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And it's very-- I think it's important to say that we saw that this Czech workers, when demounting the machine, are paying the most attention, not to destroy anything, to demount them part of the part, to put every screw in the right place, to write down which screw belongs to what part.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And then afterwards, we knew that the factory was rebuilt in months after the Germans went away by these workers.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they even found the owner was-- or one of the owners or one of the owner's children-- were here in the States.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They found him, the workers, and called him to come back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I somewhere read about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It's by the way.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And then came the time of-- of-- of building the, the machines of, of, of-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] time when everything was to be prepared to make the very specific or special part of something.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "This was the kind of the Germans were making the parts of the ammunition.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "That every factory was making one part without knowing what-- so they said this is the safest way.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we made the-- we had to make also some part.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I, I remember, I recall that this was called MU5 or something like this.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- after a while, after two months or one month or two months, most of the machines were ready.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody got his job to work on some machine.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- I got-- I, I was working on the small machine.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we have to begin to do something.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To produce.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
